<div class="case-story__chapter">
  <h2>Apple Watch</h2>
  <p>Translating the app to the Apple Watch was a logical next-step. This form factor offers at-a-glance information along with the ability to start and stop workouts. Swiping the bezel allows the user to switch between saved workouts.</p>
